body:
Noting the failures I get on my machine when running [`bazel test tensorflow/tools/quantization:quantize_graph_test`](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tools/quantization/quantize_graph_test.py):

* test_bias_add
* test_bias_add_w_fake_quant_w_min_max_vars
* test_bias_add_w_fallback_min_max_vars
* test_conv
* test_identity
* test_mat_mul_small
* test_odd_padding_problem

These are the ones that complain about numeric inaccuracy. I don't think `tensorflow/tools` is included in the CI tests, so the errors may not pop up here.
